OL,3,C'Cheaper to let police chief retire
OL,4,Cthan suspend him' - commissioner
OL,6,FA police and crime commissioner said
OL,7,Fhe accepted his chief constable's
OL,8,Fretirement despite an investigation
OL,9,Finto alleged misconduct because it was
OL,10,Fcheaper than suspending him.
OL,12,FHumberside Police chief constable Paul
OL,13,FAnderson's retirement was announced on
OL,14,F25 June after less than a year in the
OL,15,Fpost.
