OL,3,C'Cheaper to let police chief retire
OL,4,Cthan suspend him' - commissioner
OL,6,FA day later, the Office of the Police
OL,7,Fand Crime Commissioner (OPCC)
OL,8,Fannounced allegations of potential
OL,9,Fmisconduct had been referred to the
OL,10,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,11,F(IOPC) and it had begun an independent
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,FThe IOPC investigation continues,
OL,15,Fregardless of Mr Anderson's retirement.
