OL,3,C'Cheaper to let police chief retire
OL,4,Cthan suspend him' - commissioner
OL,6,FOn Thursday, Humberside's Police and
OL,7,FCrime Commissioner Jonathan Evison
OL,8,Fanswered pre-submitted questions from
OL,9,Fthe Humberside Police and Crime Panel
OL,10,F- made up of councillors and
OL,11,Findependent members - and made a media
OL,12,Fstatement on the topic afterwards.
OL,14,FIn the statement, Mr Evison said there
OL,15,Fwere two main reasons he had accepted
OL,16,FPaul Anderson's retirement.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
