OL,3,C'Cheaper to let police chief retire
OL,4,Cthan suspend him' - commissioner
OL,6,F"It secured the most advantageous
OL,7,Ffinancial position for the force that
OL,8,Fcould have been achieved when dealing
OL,9,Fwith a situation of this nature, and
OL,10,Fit allowed for us to recruit a new
OL,11,Fpermanent chief constable quickly.
OL,13,F"Recent events surrounding misconduct
OL,14,Fallegations against chief constables
OL,15,Felsewhere show it is not uncommon to
OL,16,Fsee suspensions lasting at least nine
OL,17,Fmonths before a conclusion is made,"
OL,18,Fthe statement said.
