OL,3,C'Cheaper to let police chief retire
OL,4,Cthan suspend him' - commissioner
OL,6,F"Suspended officers are entitled to
OL,7,Freceive full pay during any period of
OL,8,Fsuspension, regardless of the
OL,9,Finvestigation's conclusion.
OL,11,F"The short period of covering costs of
OL,12,Fa temporary chief constable during the
OL,13,Fnotice period is far, far less than
OL,14,Fthe costs of covering a suspension."
OL,16,FHe also reiterated that the first the
OL,17,FOPCC knew of the allegations was on 12
OL,18,FJune, and said he stood by the warm
OL,19,Fremarks he made on Mr Anderson's
OL,20,Fretirement.
