OL,3,C'Cheaper to let police chief retire
OL,4,Cthan suspend him' - commissioner
OL,6,F"I went on record to thank him for his
OL,7,F34 years of public service and his
OL,8,Fpersonal contributions to the success
OL,9,Fwe have seen in the performance of
OL,10,FHumberside Police.
OL,12,F"I stand by those comments. The force
OL,13,Fperformed well under his leadership,
OL,14,Fand I have every confidence the force
OL,15,Fwill continue to improve."
OL,17,FDuring the Police and Crime Panel
OL,18,Fmeeting, prepared answers were
OL,19,Fprovided by Mr Evison to the panel,
OL,20,Fwith copies given to the media along
OL,21,Fwith his statement.
