OL,3,C'Cheaper to let police chief retire
OL,4,Cthan suspend him' - commissioner
OL,6,F"The referral was made while Chief
OL,7,FConstable Paul Anderson was still in
OL,8,Fpost," Mr Evison said.
OL,10,FDuring the meeting, the OPCC's chief
OL,11,Fexecutive Rachel Cook gave an
OL,12,Findicative timeline for the
OL,13,Frecruitment of the next chief
OL,14,Fconstable.
OL,16,FShe said the selection process will
OL,17,Ftake place on 21 August, and that the
OL,18,FOPCC was "hopeful" of confirming the
OL,19,Fnew appointment by September "at the
OL,20,Flatest".
